main event: An unidentified flying object was reported as a bright light moving from the NW to the SE near Gainsville, Florida on 10 Nov 1969.
interesting points: The object emitted three pin-point lights that descended toward the surface,The main object moved toward the SE and disappeared,It was concluded as a balloon by the reporting officer,The report notes that several military and civilian aircraft were operating in the area at the same time,The object was described as being of unusual nature and gave observers some concern.
sighted object: a bright light with pin-point lights
